Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:46.50,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然興趣各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:46.79,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\frz11.963\pos(807,65)}不同？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.12,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}卻能友好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:52.50,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以千萬不要隨手丟棄
